1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,400
What if you could see heat?

2
00:00:02,400 --> 00:00:04,400
You can, in a way.

3
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:06,800
Infrared radiation is all around us.

4
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:10,400
It's the heat we can sense but can't see.

5
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:13,200
Cameras detect infrared differently than your skin.

6
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:14,800
Why does that matter?

7
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:20,400
While your skin feels the warmth, special cameras can visualize it, revealing hidden details.

8
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:25,600
Infrared isn't just heat; it’s a glimpse into a world we often overlook.

9
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:27,600
Curious about more hidden science?

